# ============================================================
# Vercel deployment guard for AIOS
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# This repo is a MIXED repo: it contains BOTH
#   1. the Electron desktop app  (src/, electron/, vite.config.ts, ...)
#   2. the marketing website      (landing/)
#
# Vercel MUST ONLY deploy the website (landing/).
# The root vercel.json sets outputDirectory: "landing".
# This file is a SECOND LAYER OF DEFENSE: it blocks every
# non-website path from ever reaching the Vercel build/output,
# so the Electron app can NEVER accidentally get deployed.
# ============================================================

# --- Block the entire Electron app + tooling ---
*
!landing

# Allow only the website directory and its contents
!landing/**
